title: SpaceX Launches Private Astronaut Mission to Space Station
itunes:title: SpaceX Launches Private Astronaut Mission to Space Station
description:
Bloomberg News West Coast Correspondent Ed Ludlow reports on the SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket launching the first private mission to the International Space Station sanctioned by NASA. Bloomberg News EV Reporter Sean O'Kane discusses Tesla to start production of its Cybertruck, Roadster, and Semi as announced by CEO Elon Musk at the company’s “Cyber Rodeo” on Thursday in Austin, Texas. Bloomberg Businessweek Editor Joel Weber shares some of the stories from the new issue of Businessweek Magazine. And we Drive to the Close with Lisa Erickson, Co-Head of the Public Markets Group at U.S. Bank Wealth Management.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
